attributes.title: Unsatisfied/Traumatized This app is garbage🤮🤢 🗑
attributes.review: Hello my fellow people. I just wanted to come here and write a nice and truthful review.  I really wanted  to see if this app was good. It was July 9 1956 when I downloaded the app. It’s such a shame that it had to take this long. I just really wanted to check out the app.🧚‍♂️🤳 This is one reason I wouldn't  recommend this app. So after that I decided to delete the app because it just got me in a really bad mood, but when i tried it didn’t let me. It needed a password. I tried and I tried but then it set my whole neighborhood on fire 🔥 which is so sad because know they have no where to leave and what’s even safer is that they didn’t have any food and someone came to feed us the orange bald presidents toenails. What!!!!! I was surprised. If this isn’t bad  enough they dumped the whole toilet water on my face when I was trying to clean it. I was so traumatized so I tried deleting the app again so these things would stop. I still couldn’t but then I remembered that one of my fellow people on the reviews told us the password. I put the password and it worked. Know I will pass it to those who need it. The password was Biden 2020. Such a lifesaver.🧚‍♂️✨🌟 Thanks for Listening stay safe from this app. If we could I know we would all give it a zero.

attributes.title: Not just the app that’s bad
attributes.review: When you open the app, you see our president(!) holding up what seems to be a BLM fist. Now I’m no expert but didn’t he say that black people have nothing to live for?🤔 Coming from someone who is legally 18, I can also see why people are not liking him. I can see why majority of POC think he’s terrible. Now let’s talk about my experience with the app. When I opened it, I typed in my phone number (555) 123-987. And can you believe it!!??? They didn’t accept it. I wonder why.🙃 But anyways, I hate this app, it’s ruthless just like the person who approves of this app👁👄👁(❌🧢).
